♪ When darkness falls ♪

21:59.151 --> 22:02.521
♪ Leaving shadows in the night ♪

22:02.521 --> 22:05.924
♪ Don't be afraid ♪

22:05.924 --> 22:09.561
♪ Wipe that fear from
